profile:
Since 1993, we have served the Electrical Contracting needs of the nation's capital and the Ottawa Valley.  Draper Electric Ltd. has been serving the needs of clients large and small. 

Whether it is a residential renovation, (basement wiring, upgrading your electrical panel), new home construction, or a major commercial installation, we have the skill and experience to handle the job.

Our reputation for diligence, thoroughness and quality is well known throughout the industry.
